Global Automotive Electronic Logging Device Market Insights
Automotive Electronic Logging Device Market size was valued at USD 5.7 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Automotive Electronic Logging Device Market Overview
The Automotive Electronic Logging Device (ELD) market was valued at approximately USD 4.4 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach around USD 9.1 billion by 2030, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 11.2% during the forecast period. This growth is primarily driven by the increasing adoption of ELDs to comply with government regulations, enhanced fleet management requirements, and rising demand for real-time vehicle data monitoring. The market is witnessing robust growth due to advancements in telematics technology and the increased need for fleet operators to improve efficiency, safety, and reduce operational costs.

